Čermák, who will be at the head of unified management, will be complemented by the Executive Director of Centrum Holdings Andreas Demuth.
Pavel Voparil was appointed the new joint director of the business, to whom the advertising director of both companies, Zuzana Tylčerová, is also subordinate.
Štěpán Burda became the new head of information technology.
The joint director of the editors is Vladimír Piskáček, whose team also includes the director for transformation Jakub Unger.
Adéla Pittsová was tasked with the newly established position of Marketing Director.
The independent corporate communication department is now managed by Věra Lhotská.
The joint CFO is Karel Žalud, the management of human resources for both publishing houses is led by Petra Slabá.
