Economia, owned by financier Zdeněk Bakala, has concluded a contract for the purchase of Centrum Holdings and its Czech subsidiaries at the end of April this year.
Portfolio Centrum Holdings consists of news servers Aktuálně.cz, Žena.cz, web portals, an extensive e-mail base under the brands Centrum.cz and Atlas.cz and SMB agency Najisto or the portfolio of almost two dozen other smaller websites.
Economia is the publisher of Hospodářské noviny, the news server IHNED.cz, weeklies Respekt and Ekonom and the number of printed and Internet B2B titles.
